Description: ViSAGEjr is an R shiny app developed to use **Vi**sualization and **S**imulation for **A**dvancing **G**enetics **E**ducation. The app simulates selective breeding scenarios based on user-defined inputs. It runs twenty cycles of selection and produces graphs and cartoons for visualizing phenotypic changes across generations.
